WEBVTT

00:09:58.546 --> 00:10:03.083
that more than 60 percent
of all new housing starts are being built

00:10:03.107 --> 00:10:05.725
in this flammable and dangerous mess.

00:10:07.145 --> 00:10:08.987
So when we do get a fire,

00:10:09.722 --> 00:10:13.772
large areas can literally go up in smoke.

00:10:16.363 --> 00:10:17.948
How do you feel now

00:10:19.580 --> 00:10:21.271
about the forest image

00:10:22.070 --> 00:10:23.749
that I first showed you?

00:10:23.773 --> 00:10:25.722
It scares the heck out of me.

00:10:27.729 --> 00:10:29.119
So what do we do?